sellerCard.description: Hello, I'm Hmd. I hold a Bachelor of Science degree in Graphic Design from the Aawaz Institute of Media and Management Science in Karachi. My expertise lies in graphic design, and I also excel in crafting professional WordPress websites and logo animations. I would be delighted to contribute to your projects. If you have any inquiries beforehand, please feel free to reach out. Thank you!

description.content:
Greetings! I'm Hmd, your go-to expert with over 5 years of experience in crafting exceptional websites. Whether you're dreaming of a dynamic WordPress website, a unique custom design, or an engaging blog, I'm here to bring your vision to life.


What's in Store for You:

  • Skillfully designed WordPress website, custom design, or blog
  • Impeccable 100% Mobile Responsive layout
  • Tailored features that embody your brand identity
  • Elevate your site's aesthetics with thoughtfully selected Stock Photos
  • Boost user engagement with strategically placed Opt-in Forms
  • Enhance search engine visibility with meticulous On-Page SEO
  • Ensure a secure and seamless website experience
  • Post Development Support for any future requirements
  • Video Training sessions to empower you in site management
  • Expertise with leading page builders: Elementor, Divi, WP Bakery, and more
  • Unlimited revisions for your perfect vision


Why Partner with Me?

Proven excellence with an impressive project portfolio, unwavering commitment to top-notch quality, and specialized proficiency in WordPress, design, and development. Embark on your website journey confidently and click "ORDER NOW" to create something

extraordinary together :)


HMD

questionsAndAnswers.question: What I need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I would need domain + hosting logins, logo, names of pages, content for pages and any specific instructions or layout you have in your mind.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide Hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I don't provide hosting. However, i can recommend a Wordpress friendly hosting

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer unlimited revisions?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I do provide unlimited revisions as per the scope of project. If you ask for something extra, you will have to pay for it

questionsAndAnswers.question: Support period once the order will be completed?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I respect everyone that's why I will give you free assistance of what I do for 30 DAYS once the order will be completed. Moreover, You can ask me for text and image changes once the order will be completed

reviews.comment: I love working with him and always will work with him
Thank you Sayed for your great work on my website. We really appreciate what you have made and looking forward working together again in the future!

I cannot say enough good things about Sayed and the service and product delivered. I am challenged at best with technology and he was able to take my vision and make it a reality. The turn around time was very quick and efficient. He understood what I needed and made edits as requested in a very timely fashion. In fact, I think I probably slowed down the process the most as my schedule didn't allow my responses to be as quick as they should have been. I highly recommend his services. I think there isn't a better choice for anyone to make. THANK YOU!!!!
Amazing job as always! My go to for my WordPress needs!
